        "setup": "Generate a Paragon Signing Key in your Paragon dashboard under **Settings > SDK Setup**, store the private key securely, then have your backend mint a Paragon User Token JWT for each signed-in user as described in [Installing the SDK](https://docs.useparagon.com/getting-started/installing-the-connect-sdk). Use that token with `paragon.authenticate(PROJECT_ID, USER_TOKEN)` or send it as `Authorization: Bearer <Paragon User Token>` to the REST APIs that operate on a connected user.",
